<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ユーザー登録完了</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .success-container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .message {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .back-to-top {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #2196F3;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .back-to-top:hover {
            background-color: #0b7dda;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="success-container">
        <h2>ユーザー登録完了</h2>
        <p class="message">ようこそ新規登録 <%= username %> さん</p>
        <a class="back-to-top" href="/">掲示板トップへ戻る</a>
        <p>copy write<br>なんでも掲示板</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
